==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wernerian
<hw>Wer*ne"ri*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining
to A. G. <ets>Werner</ets>, The German mineralogist and geologist, who
classified minerals according to their external characters, and
advocated the theory that the strata of the earth's crust were formed by
depositions from water; designating, or according to, Werner's
system.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wernerite</ent>⟦br⟧
